filement virtual filesystem (fvfs)
	a tree where each node is characterized by a type
	types:
		root
		device
		block
		entry

	each node has name; the name of the root node is empty - ""
	when forming a path, nodes are separated by /
	each node has metainformation associated with it

metainformation
	device
		host, port, friendly name, ?
	block
		?
	entry
		?

{"type": "ROOT", "meta": {...}, "children": [{"uuid0": {"type": "DEVICE", "meta": {"host": "...", "port": ..., "label": "..."}, "children": [...]}}]}

